Q kie tm anuj mere sath itna bura?
itna bara dhoka q die anuj kya galti thi meri maine aisa kya kia k tmne mere sath itna bura kar dia?
q meri zindagi k sath khelte rhe ? q aisa kie kya mil gya meri zindagi kharab krke?
pyar mujhse shaadi kisi or se q? 
jb mujhse shaadi kvi karni hi ni thi to q mere ghr aaye q sabse shaadi ka commitment karwaye q tmhre ghr wale v mujhse baate krte rhe?
or ek din bina mujhe kuch bole kisi or k sath engagement kaise kar sakte ho anuj kaise ?
thora v mera khayal ni aaya mera chehra thora v saamne ni aaya?
13/03/2023 ko tm engagement kie ho or us din v mujhe call kie the?
kaise aisa kaise kar sakte ho anuj tm mere sath?
kaise mai khud ko samjhau/.
itna kuch hone k baad v pagalo ki tarah tmhra wait kar rhi
gakti meri hai maine tmpe andhvishwas kia tha
bht acha sila dia tmne bht acha
